  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EEvery now and then you run into a case that despite your best efforts, is not responding to laser treatment. \u0026nbsp;Every clinician has experienced this. \u0026nbsp;You apply all your knowledge and clinical expertise, and they are still stuck in a holding pattern. \u0026nbsp;This webinar we will discuss these types of cases and how you can blend other techniques with your laser protocols, or tweak your protocols to get a breakthrough for these patients.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EJoin Dr. Chris Carraway and his special guest speaker for some Clinical Pearls and application tips, to help get past roadblocks in laser treatment. \u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022 \u0022\u003EWatch/More info\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
